## Acronyms Table
<!-- All acronyms used in project documents must appear here. Spell out the full form on first use in each document, with the acronym in parentheses. -->
| Acronym | Full Form | Context |
|---------|-----------|---------|
| RTM | Requirements Traceability Matrix | Used across all phases to track requirement-to-test linkage |
| NFR | Non-Functional Requirement | Describes system quality attributes (performance, security, etc.) |
| AC | Acceptance Criterion | A testable condition that a requirement must satisfy |
| REQ | Requirement | Prefix for all requirement IDs (format: REQ-YYYY-NNN) |
| BL | Baseline | Prefix for requirements baseline version (format: BL-YYYY-NNN) |
| SRS | Software Requirements Specification | Formal document compiling all software requirements |
